01:02:20,597 --> 01:02:22,257
<font color="yellow">Saya belum pernah mendengar novel itu sebelumnya.</font>

835
01:02:22,997 --> 01:02:24,527
<font color="yellow">Apa novel itu benar-benar ada?</font>

836
01:02:30,657 --> 01:02:32,697
<font color="yellow">Novel itu masih belum dicetak.</font>

837
01:02:34,397 --> 01:02:35,497
