<font color="yellow">untuk membalaskan dendam kedua orangtuaku.</font>

848
01:03:58,927 --> 01:04:00,797
<font color="yellow">Kakiku serasa tertanam di lumpur.</font>

849
01:04:01,127 --> 01:04:02,157
